SELECT q.qubit_id, q.qubit_name, ecc.code_type, ecp.procedure_name FROM qubits q JOIN error_correction_codes ecc ON q.qubit_id = ecc.qubit_id JOIN error_correction_procedures ecp ON ecc.code_id = ecp.code_id WHERE ecc.code_id > 2;

SELECT q.qubit_name, ecc.code_type, ecp.procedure_name FROM qubits q LEFT JOIN error_correction_codes ecc ON q.qubit_id = ecc.qubit_id LEFT JOIN error_correction_procedures ecp ON ecc.code_id = ecp.code_id;
